dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents districts in Malaysia. The Global Map Malaysia version 2 is extracted from existing topographic map of scale 1:25 000.Global Map data were developed under the cooperation of National Geospatial Information Authorities (NGIAs) of respective countries and regions.
